        *   `span.classList.add('animated-char');`: Adds the CSS class that defines the animation.
        *   `span.style.animationDelay = `${i * animationDelay}ms`;`: **This is the core of the staggered animation.** Each character's animation starts `animationDelay` milliseconds after the previous one, creating a "typewriter" or "reveal" effect.
